24d4			; Changing use of opcodes to flag is the word exists in compiled form or not.  
24d4			; This provides a means to compile uwords if required for higher performance 
24d4			; by avoiding the use of the keyword parser and just jumping directly to the code 
24d4			; Actually there is already a flag for if the code exists as binary thinking about it... 
